{"tid":2115252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭松泰會否開記者會, 炮轟林鄭強迫香港人戴口罩?","createTime":"2020-07-19T11:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T12:50:11.000Z","uid":134071,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f6c0946ebc2480ed51929713f8678ed120767b","tid":2115252,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:14:04.000Z","msg":"熱狗自稱最誠實既政治派系.<br />\n<br />\n而家, 林鄭強迫香港人係室內戴口罩. &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰會否在本星期五前(7月24日), 聯合所有熱血公民立法會參選人, call齊全港記者 (包括tvb記者, 反正tvb昨日重點報導熱血公民參選), 開大型記者招待會, 炮轟林鄭強迫香港人係室內戴口罩, 並要求香港政府取消所有強制戴口罩既措施?<br />\n<strong>如果熱血公民夠膽係本星期五前(7月24日)咁做, 我保證我係今年立法會選舉日前, 我係連登唔會再講熱狗半句壞話.</strong><br />\n<br />\n以前, 大班同長毛都夠膽開記者會反對領匯上市, 熱狗勇氣點會輸比呢兩條&quot;港奸&quot;?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9abe9e8aa8cefd0c4d33094377dbc0d93243e2","tid":2115252,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:14:12.000Z","msg":"我都係學黃洋達<br />\n<br />\n黃洋達最近話佢覺得反送中運動就係攪港獨, 要求&quot;攪手&quot;公開表明反送中運動係咪攪港獨. &nbsp;(佢話如果&quot;攪手&quot;表明反送中運動唔係攪港獨, 就代表反送中運動係支持永續基本法. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/85/1665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fprog%2F85%2F1665&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=95218cb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/85/1665</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/85/1665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fprog%2F85%2F1665&d=WPu%2B6xJKQhRrkkmyce%2F8pnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=95218cb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/85/1665</a><br />\n<br />\n不過, 公開承認攪港獨係觸犯國安法... &nbsp;反而, 開記者會要求香港政府取消所有強制戴口罩, 並沒有犯法, 熱狗點計都有著數啦."},{"pid":"cb9b1b7023c809d3999cb1c7db61324c2464b230","tid":2115252,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"熱狗咁做, 就證明自己的確係最誠實既政治派系.<br />\n<br />\n肯定會多左好多選民支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc36676ea67726872096f5f5b1aa7a2a3fc3bbf","tid":2115252,"uid":166037,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:17:35.000Z","msg":"你班仆街熱狗唔好再洗版得唔得"},{"pid":"871c2aa62674c9af05269f743bc01f938acb6e67","tid":2115252,"uid":61914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pish"},{"pid":"6cd674376edc35353c62ed8fcf65757c4fe47082","tid":2115252,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"871c2aa62674c9af05269f743bc01f938acb6e67","tid":2115252,"uid":61914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pish"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:20:02.000Z","msg":"連登唔少熱粉, 要跟鄭松泰反映下.<br />\n<br />\n一做, 就證明熱奇的確係全香港最誠實既政治派系.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4dcee2461dde6c2800b96340ac3ee6d20cde4d","tid":2115252,"uid":47810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:22:13.000Z","msg":"公衆係白痴！ 開記者會畀你班泛登仔攞嚟攻擊呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60daebdcaf51706cc09aa416f71de245d1f608a9","tid":2115252,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed4dcee2461dde6c2800b96340ac3ee6d20cde4d","tid":2115252,"uid":47810,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:22:13.000Z","msg":"公衆係白痴！ 開記者會畀你班泛登仔攞嚟攻擊呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T11:24:34.000Z","msg":"松泰已重新重視公眾<br />\n昨日話公司唔會單睇&quot;承諾否決「財政預算案」&quot;作為選擇侯選人既指引. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b67b6e44480ce572d73f2c9983ae4a1df5d3f6","tid":2115252,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"repl